Bank Austria MobileBanking
--------------------------

MobileBanking service of UniCredit Bank Austria AG as available from their
website. This is a secure app, because it's the unaltered cross-platform
mobile banking service for UniCredit customers in Austria.

This web app is neither provided nor endorsed by UniCredit Bank Austria AG.
Bank Austria online banking is available from the following URLs:
- https://mobile.bankaustria.at/ (mobile version provided by this app)
- https://online.bankaustria.at/ (desktop version for your PC)

Support requests related to the banking service should be directed to
Bank Austria at http://www.bankaustria.at/privatkunden-kontaktformular.jsp

Information related phishing and other important security announcements
are available from http://sicherheit.bankaustria.at/ and the start page
of the desktop version (see above).

This web app is not affiliated with UniCredit Bank Austria AG. The product
name, associated trade marks and the UniCredit logo may be trade marks of
UniCredit Bank Austria AG, headquartered at Schottengasse 6-8, 1010 Wien.

